{"lemma":"رِزْمَةُ","slug":"رِزْمَةُ","root":"ر.ز.م","root_slug":"ر-ز-م","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ز-م","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15412","n15413","n15414"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%B2%D9%92%D9%85%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"bundle, packet"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"loud voice"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"baby cry"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/riz.ma/","/ra.za.ma/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15412","headword_ar":"رَزْمَةٌ","root":"rzm","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see 1: ―         -b2-  and see also the next paragraph, in two places. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^akala Alr~azomapN","text_ar":"اَكَلَ الرَّزْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He ate the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajobap","text_ar":"وَجْبَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"meal that sufficed for a day and a night,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for four and twenty hours"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.)"}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n15413","headword_ar":"رِزْمَةٌ","root":"rzm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quantity remaining in a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"receptacle of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~ap","text_ar":"جُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", [a meaning said in the TA, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rdm","text_ar":"ردم"},{"kind":"text","text":", to be erroneously assigned in the K, in that art, to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ridomapN","text_ar":"رِدْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] of dates,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amounting to half thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a third,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereabout:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or, accord. to Sh, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"third part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fourth part, of a"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sack such as is called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"giraArap","text_ar":"غِرَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereabout,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh,) of dates or flour: or, accord. to Zeyd Ibn-Kuthweh, like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qawosN","text_ar":"قَوْسٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", signifying the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quantity of the fourth part of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jul~ap","text_ar":"جُلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":", of dates: (TA:) or, accord. to the Tekmileh, [the pl.]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizamN","text_ar":"رِزَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sacks called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"garaAy^ir","text_ar":"غَرَايِر"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in which is wheat:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizam","text_ar":"رِزَم"},{"kind":"text","text":"of clothes [explained in what here follows. (Mgh.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaArap","text_ar":"كَارَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bundle, put in one piece of cloth and tied up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] of clothes; (S, Msb, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what are tied up in one piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) of clothes: (TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"clothes,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other things, put together"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a bundle"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"razomapN","text_ar":"رَزْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Mgh:) IAmb explains it as meaning the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing in which are sorts"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Durawb","text_ar":"ضُرَوب"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and mixtures of clothes:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and hence the author of the K has taken a meaning assigned by him to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizomapN","text_ar":"رِزْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which, he says, is also written ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"razomapN","text_ar":"رَزْمَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", namely,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DarobN $adiydN","text_ar":"ضَرْبٌ شَدِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a vehement beating"},{"kind":"text","text":"], altering and substituting: (TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizomapN","text_ar":"رِزْمَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rizamN","text_ar":"رِزَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Mgh","K"]},{"entry_id":"n15414","headword_ar":"رَزَمَةٌ","root":"rzm","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sort of yearning cry,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a she-camel, when loving,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affecting, her young one, uttered from her throat,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fauces,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without opening her mouth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"not as loud as that which is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaniynN","text_ar":"حَنِينٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (AZ, S, TA.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"razamapN walaA dir~apN","text_ar":"رَزَمَةٌ وَلَا دِرَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A gentle yearning cry of a she-camel, and no flow of milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA xayora fiY razamapK","text_ar":"لَا خَيْرَ فِى رَزَمَةٍ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA dir~apa fiyhaA","text_ar":"لَا دِرَّةَ فِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There is no good in a gentle yearning cry of a she-camel with which is no flow of milk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K:) applied to him who promises and does not fulfil: (S, K:) or to him who causes to wish and does not act: (A, TA:) or to him who makes a show of love, or affection, without proving it to be true or without;t its being accompanied by any gift. (M, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cry of a boy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"child."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA: but not in the CK.) ―         -b3-  And, accord. to IAar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A vehement cry"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sound."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cries of beasts of prey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) A poet says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"lils~ibaAEi Hawolahu razamaho \n                      \n                     \n                        tarakuwA EamoraAna munojadilAF"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They left 'Amrán prostrate upon the ground; there being cries of the beasts of prey around him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (IB, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["AZ","S","K","TA","A"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}